@startuml Sequence_Candidate_Main_Flow
title Ứng Viên - Workflow Chính: Tìm & Nộp Đơn

actor Candidate as "👤 Ứng viên"
participant FrontEnd as "Frontend\nApp"
participant AuthService as "Auth\nService"
participant CVService as "CV\nService"
participant JobService as "Job\nService"
participant MatchingService as "Matching\nService"
participant ApplicationService as "Application\nService"
participant NotificationService as "Notification\nService"
database Database as "Database"

== 1. Đăng ký & Đăng nhập ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: 1.1 Mở app
FrontEnd -> AuthService: 1.2 POST /api/auth/dang-ky-ung-vien\n(email, password, fullName)
AuthService -> Database: 1.3 Tạo tai_khoan & ung_vien
Database --> AuthService: 1.4 Return taiKhoanId
AuthService --> FrontEnd: 1.5 Return JWT token
FrontEnd --> Candidate: 1.6 Đăng ký thành công

Candidate -> FrontEnd: 1.7 Đăng nhập (email, password)
FrontEnd -> AuthService: 1.8 POST /api/auth/dang-nhap
AuthService -> Database: 1.9 Verify credentials
Database --> AuthService: 1.10 OK
AuthService --> FrontEnd: 1.11 Return JWT token
FrontEnd --> Candidate: 1.12 Logged in ✅

== 2. Tạo CV & Thêm Kỹ năng ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: 2.1 Click "Tạo CV mới"
FrontEnd -> CVService: 2.2 POST /api/cvs\n(tenCv, moTa)
CVService -> Database: 2.3 Create ho_so_cv
Database --> CVService: 2.4 Return cvId
CVService --> FrontEnd: 2.5 CV created
FrontEnd --> Candidate: 2.6 Hiển thị form CV

Candidate -> FrontEnd: 2.7 Thêm thông tin\n(kinh nghiệm, học vấn)
FrontEnd -> CVService: 2.8 POST /api/cvs/{cvId}/hoc-van-kn
CVService -> Database: 2.9 Create chi_tiet_cv
Database --> CVService: 2.10 OK
CVService --> FrontEnd: 2.11 Return
FrontEnd --> Candidate: 2.12 Thêm thành công

Candidate -> FrontEnd: 2.13 Thêm kỹ năng
FrontEnd -> CVService: 2.14 POST /api/cvs/{cvId}/skills\n(skillId, thanhThaoDo)
CVService -> Database: 2.15 Create ct_ky_nang_hs
Database --> CVService: 2.16 OK
CVService --> FrontEnd: 2.17 Return
FrontEnd --> Candidate: 2.18 Kỹ năng thêm ✅

Candidate -> FrontEnd: 2.19 Upload PDF CV
FrontEnd -> CVService: 2.20 POST /api/cvs/{cvId}/upload-file\n(file.pdf)
CVService -> Database: 2.21 Update fileCvUrl
Database --> CVService: 2.22 OK
CVService --> FrontEnd: 2.23 Return URL
FrontEnd --> Candidate: 2.24 Upload xong ✅

== 3. Tìm Kiếm Công Việc ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: 3.1 Click "Tìm việc làm"
FrontEnd -> JobService: 3.2 GET /api/jobs?keyword=java&page=0&size=10\n(filters: location, salary, etc)
JobService -> Database: 3.3 Query tin_tuyen_dung
Database --> JobService: 3.4 Return list of jobs
JobService --> FrontEnd: 3.5 Jobs list (20 results)
FrontEnd --> Candidate: 3.6 Hiển thị tìm kiếm

Candidate -> FrontEnd: 3.7 Chọn 1 job
FrontEnd -> MatchingService: 3.8 GET /api/matching/score\n(cvId, jobId)
MatchingService -> Database: 3.9 Get CV skills & Job requirements
Database --> MatchingService: 3.10 skills, requirements
MatchingService -> MatchingService: 3.11 Calculate match score\n(80%)
MatchingService --> FrontEnd: 3.12 Return score
FrontEnd --> Candidate: 3.13 Hiển thị match score

Candidate -> FrontEnd: 3.14 Xem chi tiết job
FrontEnd -> JobService: 3.15 GET /api/jobs/{jobId}
JobService -> Database: 3.16 Get tin_tuyen_dung details
Database --> JobService: 3.17 Return job details
JobService --> FrontEnd: 3.18 Job details
FrontEnd --> Candidate: 3.19 Hiển thị đầy đủ

== 4. Nộp Đơn Ứng Tuyển ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: 4.1 Click "Nộp đơn"
FrontEnd -> FrontEnd: 4.2 Validate CV selected
FrontEnd -> ApplicationService: 4.3 POST /api/applications\n(tinTuyenDungId, hoSoCvId, thuNgo)
ApplicationService -> ApplicationService: 4.4 Check duplicate\nDuplicateApplicationException
ApplicationService -> Database: 4.5 Create don_ung_tuyen
Database --> ApplicationService: 4.6 Return id
ApplicationService -> Database: 4.7 Create lich_su_trang_thai\n(MOI → REVIEW)
Database --> ApplicationService: 4.8 OK
ApplicationService --> FrontEnd: 4.9 Application submitted
FrontEnd --> Candidate: 4.10 Nộp đơn thành công ✅

ApplicationService -> NotificationService: 4.11 Notify Recruiter\n(New application)
NotificationService -> Database: 4.12 Create thong_bao\n(UNG_TUYEN_TAO_MOI)
Database --> NotificationService: 4.13 OK
NotificationService --> ApplicationService: 4.14 Return

== 5. Theo Dõi Đơn ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: 5.1 Click "Đơn của tôi"
FrontEnd -> ApplicationService: 5.2 GET /api/applications\n(page=0, size=10)
ApplicationService -> Database: 5.3 Query don_ung_tuyen (taiKhoanId)
Database --> ApplicationService: 5.4 Return list
ApplicationService --> FrontEnd: 5.5 Applications list
FrontEnd --> Candidate: 5.6 Hiển thị danh sách đơn

Candidate -> FrontEnd: 5.7 Chọn 1 đơn để xem chi tiết
FrontEnd -> ApplicationService: 5.8 GET /api/applications/{appId}\nE Authorization check
ApplicationService -> Database: 5.9 Get don_ung_tuyen details
Database --> ApplicationService: 5.10 Return details
ApplicationService --> FrontEnd: 5.11 Application details
FrontEnd --> Candidate: 5.12 Hiển thị chi tiết đơn

Candidate -> FrontEnd: 5.13 Xem "Lịch sử trạng thái"
FrontEnd -> ApplicationService: 5.14 GET /api/applications/{appId}/history\n(page=0, size=10)
ApplicationService -> Database: 5.15 Query lich_su_trang_thai
Database --> ApplicationService: 5.16 Return status history
ApplicationService --> FrontEnd: 5.17 Status history
FrontEnd --> Candidate: 5.18 Hiển thị timeline\n(MOI → REVIEW → PHONG_VAN)

== 6. Lịch Phỏng Vấn ==

Recruiter -> NotificationService: 6.1 Tạo lịch phỏng vấn\nD9: POST /api/interviews
NotificationService -> Database: 6.2 Create lich_phong_van
Database --> NotificationService: 6.3 OK
NotificationService -> NotificationService: 6.4 Send notification
NotificationService --> Candidate: 6.5 Thông báo phỏng vấn

Candidate -> FrontEnd: 6.6 Xem "Lịch phỏng vấn"
FrontEnd -> ApplicationService: 6.7 GET /api/interviews\n(applicationId)
ApplicationService -> Database: 6.8 Query lich_phong_van
Database --> ApplicationService: 6.9 Return interviews
ApplicationService --> FrontEnd: 6.10 Interview list
FrontEnd --> Candidate: 6.11 Hiển thị lịch phỏng vấn

== 7. Thông Báo & Dashboard ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: 7.1 Click "Thông báo"
FrontEnd -> NotificationService: 7.2 GET /api/notifications\n(page=0, size=20)
NotificationService -> Database: 7.3 Query thong_bao (taiKhoanId)
Database --> NotificationService: 7.4 Return notifications
NotificationService --> FrontEnd: 7.5 Notification list
FrontEnd --> Candidate: 7.6 Hiển thị thông báo

Candidate -> FrontEnd: 7.7 Click "Dashboard"
FrontEnd -> ApplicationService: 7.8 GET /api/dashboard/candidate
ApplicationService -> Database: 7.9 Get statistics\n(total apps, pending, accepted)
Database --> ApplicationService: 7.10 Return stats
ApplicationService --> FrontEnd: 7.11 Dashboard data
FrontEnd --> Candidate: 7.12 Hiển thị dashboard\n(Đơn: 5 | Đang xem: 3 | Phỏng vấn: 1)

note over Candidate, Database
  **Quy trình hoàn tất**
  1. ✅ Đăng ký & Đăng nhập
  2. ✅ Tạo CV & Thêm kỹ năng
  3. ✅ Tìm kiếm công việc
  4. ✅ Nộp đơn ứng tuyển
  5. ✅ Theo dõi đơn
  6. ✅ Xem lịch phỏng vấn
  7. ✅ Nhận thông báo & Dashboard
end note

@enduml
